casebody.data:
Hyman Marcus et al. v. Austin Associates, Inc., et al.

(Republished)

Motion for a stay dismissed with leave to renew upon a proper notice of motion served upon all the attorneys for all the defendants-respondents. The order of this court, entered on March 8, 1962, is vacated. Concur — Rabin, J. P., Valente, Stevens, Eager and Bergan, JJ.
